{"tid":2213846,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(因鼓勵藍絲督灰而招致報應) 國泰裁員序幕｜內部估算過剩員工達6,800人","createTime":"2020-09-23T00:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T12:51:04.000Z","uid":65328,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2da6be4d9d8cf4c154be8c35226a945159f289e5","tid":2213846,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:06:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200923/XR6IKAEW3BCNJJNA4A2ZCRAOTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200923%2FXR6IKAEW3BCNJJNA4A2ZCRAOTU%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I21SbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=e0c6f274\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200923%2FXR6IKAEW3BCNJJNA4A2ZCRAOTU%2F&h=a7dee475\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200923/XR6IKAEW3BCNJJNA4A2ZCRAOTU/</a><br />\n<br />\n國泰裁員序幕｜內部估算過剩員工達6,800人 港龍機師倡「半支薪」避開刀 管理層：持開放態度<br />\n國泰（293）表明旗下兩大航空公司不會申請次輪「保就業」計劃，掀起裁員序幕。據國泰消息人士引述內部管理人員的推算，目前國泰及港龍過剩前線員工數目至少達6,800人。多個工會本月先後與集團會面，其中港龍機師工會向國泰港龍提交五大建議，包括未來一年推行月薪減半的「半支薪計劃」（Half Pay Leave Scheme）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年鼓勵藍絲督灰呀啦， 兼且買埋快運， double kill.  上年鬼佬ceo有良心有好報， 唔肯炒香港人員工寧願辭職， 今年就可以睇住間紅色國泰幾咁折墮。 新上任ceo肯做劊子手， 就報應黎， 做史上業績最差ceo,  寫入cv."},{"pid":"33f82e42542ed33716551c252586d71fae3a5b07","tid":2213846,"uid":65328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:08:10.000Z","msg":"有後勤員工認為香港快運在申請名單內，意味該公司短期內不會裁員，對國泰及港龍的員工有欠公允。<br />\n<br />\n上年炒香港人員工又唔見你出黎嘈"},{"pid":"67b8b0474096516f666f6d127ee042c03132ad88","tid":2213846,"uid":222238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:08:21.000Z","msg":"一定要壯大黃色經濟圈, 今次黎一次大洗牌"},{"pid":"b58d32ceabda45016238432b566cffe18172509e","tid":2213846,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:10:13.000Z","msg":"剃人頭者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi